CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 3, 1965, pg. 6, reads: " Wed 25 Years - Mr. and Mrs. Andrew Woods were the honorees at a reception on the occasion of their 25th wedding anniversary, held at the home of their niece and nephew, Mr. and Mrs. Willie A. Fuller of Lincoln Ave. Friends showered the honorees with many lovely gifts. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Mr. and Mrs. Andrew Woods cutting twenty-fifth anniversary sheet cake in home of Mr. and Mrs. Willie A. Fuller, Lincoln Avenue
